{"tid":1471868,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(大件事)大部分MTR站係無消防花灑系統","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T05:03:29.000Z","uid":14908,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"6f838ab4ef8d7dec5d1496de90512286768cf4e5","tid":1471868,"uid":14908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"8月11日本人在葵芳站打算落車回家<br />\n但是在站外竟然有大量防暴在外<br />\n我立刻回月台，還有叫其他人盡快上車<br />\n誰不知道一會兒後，警察在室內發放催淚彈<br />\n那些煙霧是有攻上月台的<br />\n假如港鐵站有消防花灑裝置<br />\n根本催淚煙就不能攻上月台<br />\n我本來也不知道地鐵站是沒有消防花灑裝置<br />\n直至這件事發生我才發現葵芳沒有這個裝置<br />\n在上網查一些資訊，只有15個站是有這個裝置<br />\n假如地鐵站有火觸發生<br />\n係咪只能依靠消防喉轆和消防栓<br />\n要等待消防員到場才能解決<br />\n請大家幫呢個post推上熱門<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201501/07/P201501070385.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201501%2F07%2FP201501070385.htm&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3cmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=7049cdf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201501/07/P201501070385.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20150107/mobile/bkn-20150107131850735-0107_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20150107%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20150107131850735-0107_00822_001.html&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3cmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=c7c0d126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20150107/mobile/bkn-20150107131850735-0107_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0fd4337d14c3805dd5c9dbfefcf352a2e956b73e","tid":1471868,"uid":35090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:43:35.000Z","msg":"有用，推"},{"pid":"f8588cca94cb7bf2ba8f81ed474216cabdb10361","tid":1471868,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg